etics world\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite Ingebrigtsen's victory over Kerr in their initial heat last year, it was the 26-year-old Scot who triumphed when it counted, clinching the title in the final.\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen's victory\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"their initial heat\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"the 26-year-old Scot\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr's winning time of 3:29.38 edged out Ingebrigtsen for the gold at the championships by a mere 0.27 seconds, leaving the Norwegian competitor disappointed.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9995163303059283, \"rank\": 0.00045771103026617154, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr's winning time\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"3:29.38\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 559}, {\"ngram\": \"the championships\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"a mere 0.27 seconds\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Post-race comments from the 2023 event saw Ingebrigtsen cite illness for his lacklustre performance and boldly claim he could beat Kerr \\\"blindfolded\\\".\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Post-race comments\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 event\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 691}, 